title: Geri Allen, renowned pianist, composer and Monterey Jazz Festival performer
tags: The Complete Concert By The Sea
fulltitle: Geri Allen, renowned pianist, composer and Monterey Jazz Festival performer
description: Co-Producers of "The Complete Concert By The Sea," Dir. Jazz Studies, Univ. of Pittsburgh and Senior Advisor to the Erroll Garner Jazz Project, speaks about the original "Concert By The Sea," performing it and Erroll's peers.
